### **4. 26_StreamFlowBoard**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes streaming numerical input as a live-updating chart with customizable refresh rate.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamFlowBoard - Real-Time Data Plotting Tool

StreamFlowBoard is built for visualizing dynamic metrics in dashboards, experiments, or test rigs.

## Features
- Live scrollable chart  
- Refresh rate control  
- Built on Matplotlib  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_StreamFlowBoard.git
cd 26_StreamFlowBoard
python visualize.py
